Undoped and doped BCNDs were analyzed using photo luminescence spectroscopy to discover their fluorescence behavior. The emission and excitation spectra of BCNDs were dependent on the dopants. Maximum emission intensity of undoped and doped BCNDs were observed at 435 nm (undoped) (Fig. S.9), 400 nm (N-doped) (
                        Fig. 2

                        ), 435 nm (B-doped) (Fig. S.10) and 445 nm
